Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:26.88,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,Under the skies of blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:32.92,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,Beyond the clouds of white,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:38.31,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,You'll find the blue of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:43.41,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,In the whiteness of the dragon's belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:49.63,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,In the blackness of the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:55.31,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,The red light of the fires
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.43,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,In the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:14.77,Titles,,0,0,0,,The Door to a New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare they do that right in front of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:44.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}exactly{\i0} why I was against Chor Rubor and Chor Caput being disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't have Chor Tempest be the only ones we can depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gather all the troops and the Simile!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:54.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reconnaissance Simile and the cruising Simile! All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:02.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope you realize that fighting leads absolutely nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:27.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come one, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:29.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over here, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said no playing on the Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:43.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah c'mon, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well... because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:54.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:57.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Booooou...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's making a noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like, "booooou!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like, "booooou!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:09.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Booooou..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Told ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's something inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:00.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,So the day has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you please give us a little more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay for us to come after we've finished our meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did the meeting end badly? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia is the symbol of the Simulacrum Theocracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:29.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the authorities have been enjoying her continuing silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:33.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if she decides to act... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I take no pleasure in warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:41.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,To bring her here for a reason like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't fathom what Her Eminence is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:47.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:16.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never in {\i1}history{\i0} has anyone flown out in a Simoun without orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you no sense of responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:23.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our responsibility as Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pride in what we are. That which each of us bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was that all that you wanted to say to us, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that case, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, those little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,And... Rodoreamon and Alti as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too, Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Couldn't sleep, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, it looks like everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:56.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Messis{\i0} will bear Onashia to her destination. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you care to accompany her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,And would you like to know about... another world? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...come along, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:16.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those we have will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...isn't the word I'd use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kind of, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:56.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it's sweet too... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bit it's not a taste I really hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...be able to finish eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Dunno."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,You never say that any more, Limone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:18.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I started thinking about things more, and I feel like... there isn't much I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:27.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more I think, the more confused I become.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd best get going as soon as we've finished eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:52.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her Eminence has ordered us to avoid "flying recklessly."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia-sama is currently resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder how "another world" is connected to all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel really uneasy around the High Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Defence Minister is kind of a bastard, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:47.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her Eminence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmm, how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop treating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:10.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,This war... it makes such obvious things hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You have something you wish to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You told me that you can hear Mamiina's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:28.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:30.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what about my comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have their souls... been set free?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:44.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} are the one who wants to be set free, aren't you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:51.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,You keep trying to live close to the time and place where your friends died. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yet at the same time, you long to escape to a place far away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems that we have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:59.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why have we come to the Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,"The Door to a New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the melody played by that music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:21.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the unsuspected goal of those who perished here.  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:21.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place was once the training ground for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor... Dextra? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:33.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru, your grandfather was the regina of that choir. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grandpa... was the regina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened back then? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,When do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,On the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything just poured into me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,When I looked inside the helical motor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,it was as though I saw someone's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or some{\i1}thing's{\i0} memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's in there is a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:23.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we can understand about it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:55.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,We became obsessed by the Ri Maajon... by the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:59.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that was because the Simoun were all that we had to rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. If the Simoun had never existed in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:10.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or if they had existed, but no one had been around to explain how they worked, what would have happened?  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We brought them! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:36.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A long, long time ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...there was a civilization vastly more advanced than ours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:02.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is said that the Simoun are relics from those days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:08.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,But an unending series of wars broke out, and left the world in ruins. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,With everything destroyed, the land became worthless,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:14.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,and further war became pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:16.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun were of no use to the starving masses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,and the reason for their existence was forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:24.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,The people could do nothing more than wait for death to claim them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:36.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then, from the sky, it is said that a Simoun appeared from another world. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:40.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Within it rode a pair of maidens, descending from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:48.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They introduced themselves as "Simoun sibyllae."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,they imparted the secret of the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ultimate Ri Maajon transports you to another {\i1}time{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:06.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is a divine gift that we have been granted—a great "what if?".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:13.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the people of that time had been told that there would be another war...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the Simoun didn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I wouldn't exist, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:25.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If, at that time, someone had been able to prevent people from relying on the Simoun...{\i0} 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if I didn't exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,then this pain I feel wouldn't have to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:39.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...then our present, with all its extreme distress and poverty, might be very different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,By travelling through time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we can take this power of "what if?" to another age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:48.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is the purpose of the Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,and of the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Travelling across time and space...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:55.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:56.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then this "Chor Dextra" that Grandpa commanded...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra was a choir created specifically to complete the Emerald Ri Maajon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:09.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someone you all know very well once belonged to that choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:10.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:17.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,She is the only surviving member of Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. I finally realised...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:40.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that everything happened because {\i1}I{\i0} started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:04.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about what you said before, Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:08.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,About "what if the Simoun didn't exist?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:10.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they had never existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:11.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:15.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then... I would never have met everyone in Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:20.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,And... I wouldn't have met you either, Dominura. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, why am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,U-ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:41.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're... happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:47.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:54.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:58.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,You still don't know where we're gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:04.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura has probably completed the Emerald Ri Maajon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that she is alive, in some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:08.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:14.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura and Sibylla Limone are alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do not believe that I am mistaken about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria might be too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that it's possible that Amuria is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:33.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon is the one hope given to us by Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:40.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether it takes you into the future or into the past is beyond anyone's control.  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:46.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, the Simoun exist through the will of Tempus Spatium. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:50.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it is not likely that the gods would err.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:56.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium will undoubtedly open the door to the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:58.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to entrust this to you:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:18.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun from the {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:24.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:27.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,What... what is this? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:29.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:31.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:37.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock high! Five ancient Simoun, closing in fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:38.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
